            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#">Sahiplen</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="https://keos.kocaali.bel.tr/imardurumu/index.aspx" target="_blank">E-İmar</a></li>
